{"tid":2058042,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「總加速師」庚子年的瘋狂中國資深傳媒人 - 呂月","createTime":"2020-06-10T00:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T00:51:49.000Z","uid":80972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"130ccef45e0c239d316b005c3ae03c64f8edbb3e","tid":2058042,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:45:14.000Z","msg":"港版安全法是壓在習近平身上的最後一根稻草，它帶來的是中共對香港更為殘酷的血洗，也會帶來香港人更為持久的、堅韌的反抗。1979和美國建交後的鄧小平說過四句話：一、跟着美國跑的國家都富了；二、跟着蘇聯跑的國家都窮了；三、跟着美國跑的國家都民主了；四、跟着蘇聯跑的國家都獨裁了。41年後只需要把蘇聯換成習近平，結論都成立。<br />\n<br />\n習近平毀掉香港這個世界的金融中心、貿易中心，就是毀掉中國，是他在中共王朝末日路上的狂奔。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200610&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20934386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200610%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20934386&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=2fea2d15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200610%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20934386&h=bea607e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200610&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20934386</a>"},{"pid":"d267fbd2f06c59f9b118027d0e8fd523e16f5bdb","tid":2058042,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dadad3d36bd3f432d646437c84c96570494f26bd","tid":2058042,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:45:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"865e988847694d518b5cfaceb2e52df7ff82d8d5","tid":2058042,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414e077f5d8d315dc1f438cd104a5b0f66278385","tid":2058042,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy